This is a natural segue into things we do in R.

00:09:14.099 --> 00:09:17.280
One of the other things that's very tempting to do when you know the tools that we all

00:09:17.280 --> 00:09:21.979
know is to say, oh, oh, I'm going to take your workflow, and I'm going to help you fix

00:09:21.979 --> 00:09:22.979
it.

