We can do that with the right table function.

00:13:12.419 --> 00:13:17.640
And the thing I would like to point out is the two lower parameters, table style and

00:13:17.640 --> 00:13:18.640
table name.

00:13:18.640 --> 00:13:23.520
This is where we get named tables in Excel by using this feature.

00:13:23.520 --> 00:13:28.440
So if they have built in their spreadsheet formulas already, referencing tables and

00:13:28.440 --> 00:13:32.479
columns as I have been trying to encourage them to do, we can replace their data.

